Description:
As a developer I want to create standard image In order to track all packages and versions in use by my stack

Acceptance criteria:
Stories:
Given a new image
When I push it to a ECR
Then it will get scanned with all security best practices

AND

Given a new EC2 (ECS) instance
When it gets created
Then this stable version (which should not be hard-coded)

Technical notes:
This exercise can be executed using the ECR and EC2 modules
Images should be tagged to be used
